faqs.question: Can I make an online appointment and pay later

alternateQuestions.question: When do you expect to pay fee for an appointment

faqs.label: Can I make an online appointment and pay later

answer.text: We do not provide this facility now. Our aim is to assist you in obtaining a confirmed appointment with a doctor on a selected time slot and date.

faqs.question: Can I make an online booking with my credit card for somebody else

alternateQuestions.question: How to pay consultation fee for somebody else appointment

faqs.label: Can I make an online booking with my credit card for somebody else

faqs.question: Can I reschedule an online appointment

alternateQuestions.question: How to modify an online appointment

faqs.label: Can I reschedule an online appointment

answer.text: Yes, you can reschedule an online appointment. Please type Modify Appointment to reschedule.

faqs.question: Can I cancel an appointment booked through online

alternateQuestions.question: Is it possible to cancel an appointment booked through online

faqs.label: Can I cancel an appointment booked through online

answer.text: Yes, please type modify appointment to cancel your confirmed appointment.

alternateQuestions.question: Can we book an appointment virtually

answer.text: When you visit a doctor and seek an appointment for a future date, this can be done at his location by making payment in cash. The booking charges in case of onsite appointment are less in comparison to the online appointments as we do not require to pay to the payment gateway provider in case of cash receipts.

faqs.question: What are the time restrictions for cancelling an appointment

alternateQuestions.question: Is there any time extent for cancelling an appointment

faqs.label: What are the time restrictions for cancelling an appointment

answer.text: You can cancel an appointment immediately following the booking of an appointment till a day prior to the appointment date.
